<H3> <TI>   Bilateral Expert Groups Meet in Moscow </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bilateral Expert Groups Meet in Moscow </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Disarmament on the Agenda </H4>

<F P=102> LD0405135794 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1304 GMT 4 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0405135794 </F>
