<H4>    Balladur Signals Possible Resumption </H4>

<F P=102> LD1005110994 Paris France-2 Teletext in French 1008 GMT 10 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1005110994 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris France-2 Teletext </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


