<F P=100> NEAR EAST &amp; SOUTH ASIA </F>
<F P=101> PAKISTAN </F>
<H3> <TI>   Stronger Measures Against Drug Smugglers urged </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Stronger Measures Against Drug Smugglers urged </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94WD0311B Peshawar MASHRIQ in Urdu 8 Mar 94 p 6 </F>
<F P=103> 94WD0311B </F>
<F P=104>  Peshawar MASHRIQ </F>
<F P=105>  Urdu </F>


<TEXT>
CSO 

<F P=106> [Editorial: "We Need Full Measures to Eliminate Narcotics"] </F>
  [Text] Among the Benazir government's priorities, in 
addition to establishing law and order, eradicating 
unemployment, is the elimination of narcotic trade and taking 
action against smugglers. Thus, a decision was made to take 
steps to eliminate drug smuggling and the lists prepared during 
the caretaker government were also acquired. This system of drug 
smuggling in Pakistan has been going on for many years. In 
addition to affecting our nation's economy and prosperity, it 
hinders implementation of law and order. It can also prove 
destructive to the new generation. About 12 or 15 years ago, the 
drug abuse was limited to hashish and opium, however, after the 
Soviet interference in Afghanistan, heroin also joined this 
list. Its trade spread because its price has the secret of 
changing people from rags to riches. Therefore, people who 
hanker for money and disregard fear of God use various tricks to 
make money. As the result of it, the drug trade has also reached 
educational institutions and even female students, in addition 
to male students. Although all the Pakistani governments during 
the last few years have taken some steps to end drug smuggling, 
there have been difficulties in totally controlling narcotics 
trade because of involvement of some influential persons in 
drugs, especially hashish and heroin, smuggling. Heroin worth 
millions of rupees is seized every year, however, the persons 
involved in this trade are so influential and they have so many 
contacts that they manage to escape the law. It is hoped that 
the present government which has the mandate from the majority 
of our people will pay attention to this evil without any 
leniency or favoritism, and will leave no stone unturned in 
totally eliminating this evil. Peace-loving citizens and 
patriots will fully cooperate with the government to eradicate 
this curse. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

